    "text": "This translation key is used to display a label for rooms that can only be viewed, typically in a filtering or search interface. It appears as a filter option on pages like the Home page's Filter section, allowing users to select view-only rooms. Translators should aim for an accurate and descriptive phrase that maintains the intended accessibility and functionality of the UI component.",
